# [ASDF](../wg/asdf.html)

## Summary

The ASDF Working Group met at IETF 126 in Vienna. The session covered administrative updates, status reviews of active working group drafts, and technical presentations on compact SDF representations, digital twin modeling, and a new proposal for embedding privacy properties within SDF schemas. The working group also discussed future plans for WG Last Calls (WGLC), upcoming interim meetings, and methods to make SDF more accessible to developers through code examples and documentation.

